      "message": "Line 315: 🟡 Suggestion: `startedActivities` is decremented blindly in `onActivityStopped`, so an unexpected lifecycle imbalance could make the counter negative and prevent future foreground detection. Clamp the counter and only record background time on a real transition to zero. Suggested fix:\n```suggestion\nstartedActivities \u003d (startedActivities - 1).coerceAtLeast(0)\nif (startedActivities \u003d\u003d 0) {\n    backgroundTimestamp \u003d android.os.SystemClock.elapsedRealtime()\n}\n```",
